des:
Good Afternoon is a skill that greets you in return and shares a wonderful quote to encourage and motivate you. It would reply with a randomly selected different quote each time.

Good afternoon provides a nice experience interacting with Alexa and get motivated.

To start, just say "Alexa, open Good Afternoon".
